         Per CLAUDE.md §8 FULL applies.
      📖 PROTOCOL STEPS TO EXECUTE: Steps 0–10 below; quality gates at 9.5.
      Proceeding with Step 0...
      ```
    </step>

    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Read `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md` and confirm task 007 status is 🔲, dependencies
      are `001, 003`, wave is P1-G5, parallel-safe = ✅ (with 008). Verify
